  "Lore": {
    "Backstory": "The Flash AMG GT Black Series is Mercedes-AMG at their most unhinged. They took the already extreme AMG GT and turned everything to 11. The hand-built 4.0L twin-turbo V8 now features a flat-plane crankshaft, making it rev higher and scream louder than any Mercedes has a right to. 720 horsepower through the rear wheels alone. That massive wing generates 400kg of downforce at speed. The wide body exists purely to accommodate the massive tires needed to put all that power down. It set the production car lap record at the Nurburgring because of course it did. This isn't a road car with track potential - it's a GT3 race car with license plates.",
